metadata.name: XmAIs 2023
metadata.description: We want to celebrate with you this Christmas and also thank you for sharing the journey with us during 2022. With the best wishes from FLOC*, we are pleased to offer you a special NFT for the start of 2023. This small asset is the result of the collaboration of the members from the FLOC* collective with one of the sensations of 2022 in the creative fields, artificial neural networks. We are amazed by Artificial Intelligence, ‚ù§ AIs, and yet, we love Collective Intelligence even more.
